# Frontend Rules

## Keep It Simple

- Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS only - no frameworks
- Use semantic HTML elements
- Inline styles are fine for this POC
- CDN dependencies over local files

## Educational UI Standards

- Clean, intuitive design
- Clear error messages for users
- Loading states for API calls
- Accessible form controls

## File Organization

- Static files in `src/Aula.Api/wwwroot/`
- Use `dotnet run` for local development
- Keep HTML files focused and readable




